#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:1 of
msgid "Generate a mostly low rank matrix with bell-shaped singular values"
msgstr "生成一个具有钟形奇异值的 mostly low rank 矩阵"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:3 of
msgid ""
"Most of the variance can be explained by a bell-shaped curve of width "
"effective_rank: the low rank part of the singular values profile is::"
msgstr ""
"大多数方差可以通过宽度为 effective_rank 的钟形曲线来解释：奇异值分布的低"
"秩部分为："

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:8 of
msgid "The remaining singular values' tail is fat, decreasing as::"
msgstr "剩余的奇异值尾部是厚尾的，按如下方式递减："

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:12 of
msgid ""
"The low rank part of the profile can be considered the structured signal "
"part of the data while the tail can be considered the noisy part of the "
"data that cannot be summarized by a low number of linear components "
"(singular vectors)."
msgstr ""
"分布中的低秩部分可以视为数据的结构化信号部分，而尾部则可视为无法通过少量"
"线性成分（奇异向量）概括的数据噪声部分。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:17 of
msgid "This kind of singular profiles is often seen in practice, for instance:"
msgstr "这种奇异值分布在实际中经常出现，例如："

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:18 of
msgid "gray level pictures of faces"
msgstr "人脸的灰度图像"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:19 of
msgid "TF-IDF vectors of text documents crawled from the web"
msgstr "从网络爬取的文本文档的 TF-IDF 向量"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:21 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <sample_generators>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <sample_generators>`。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.datasets.make_low_rank_matrix.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:23 of
msgid "The number of samples."
msgstr "样本数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:25 of
msgid "The number of features."
msgstr "特征数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:27 of
msgid ""
"The approximate number of singular vectors required to explain most of "
"the data by linear combinations."
msgstr "用线性组合解释大部分数据所需的奇异向量近似数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:30 of
msgid ""
"The relative importance of the fat noisy tail of the singular values "
"profile."
msgstr "奇异值分布中厚噪声尾部的相对重要性。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:33 of
msgid ""
"Determines random number generation for dataset creation. Pass an int for"
" reproducible output across multiple function calls. See :term:`Glossary "
"<random_state>`."
msgstr ""
"决定数据集创建时的随机数生成方式。传入一个整数可以在多次函数调用中获得可"
"重现的输出。详见 :term:`术语表 <random_state>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_low_rank_matrix:37 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的分块大小"

